The burial of Mrs. Clara An­irah (nee Pemu), who died on January 7, 2022, at 95 years, has been scheduled for Feb­ruary 26, 2022, in Adagbrass, Elume, Sapele Local Govern­ment Area of Delta State. According to the son of the deceased and the member representing Sapele in Delta State House of Assembly, Fe­lix Anirah, the funeral service holds at St. Theresa’s Catholic Church, Adagbrassa, Elume by 9 am. Interment takes place at her compound in Adag­brass, Elume at 12 noon. She is survived by seven children among whom is Fe­lix Anirah, grand and great grandchildren. NiMET Warns Of Extreme Heats As Temperature Rises Across States Yobe Commends AFRYDEV For Training GBV Survivors Anirah was until her death a devout Christian